# CI fixture cache (used by tests/conftest.py + .github/workflows/ci.yml).
# Built lazily per CI run; checked-in copies would rot against the code
# that produces them. The .test_durations file IS checked in -- it's
# stable across runs and only updated intentionally via --store-durations.
.scored_ws_cache/
